      "text": "わぁ……東京の神社はこんなに人がいるんですね\n星見市の神社よりもずっと大きいし……",
      "startTime": 8.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "出店も沢山あるから、ゆっくり見て回ろうか",
      "startTime": 12.7995237033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 16.3595236938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "食べもの以外も沢山あるんですね\nお祭りみたいで楽しいです",
      "startTime": 19.8271430016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あのTシャツ……",
      "startTime": 22.8028567315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
