    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……",
      "startTime": 25.6901129008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 28.8271430016
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃？\nさっきからTシャツを見てるけど、気になるのか？",
      "startTime": 30.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "生活も仕事もずっと一緒だったからだと思うんですけど\n最近、月ストのみんなの影響を\n受けている気がするんです",
      "startTime": 41.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 44.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "Tシャツのドーナツから変な猫が顔を出している絵が\nなんだか可愛い……ような……気がします……？",
      "startTime": 48.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 55.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんで疑問形なんだ……\nとりあえず、芽衣と沙季の影響を受けてるのは分かった",
      "startTime": 58.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 62.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "む……なんでニヤニヤしてるんですか",
      "startTime": 62.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 66.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん、からかうつもりはないから",
      "startTime": 66.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……",
      "startTime": 70.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 72.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃も、周りのみんなと関わって）\n（少しずつ変わっていってるんだな）",
      "startTime": 75.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "もう少し見て回ってもいいですか？\nその……せっかくなので",
      "startTime": 81.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 85.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
