      "text": "ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 108.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 110.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "私、アイドルになった頃は、自分をお姉ちゃんや\nライバルのアイドルと比べてばかりいたんです",
      "startTime": 115.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 118.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "それはだんだん落ち着いてきて……そしたら今度は\n星見のみんなと比べるようになってきたんです",
      "startTime": 124.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 128.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "特に月ストのみんなはずっと一緒にいるから余計に……",
      "startTime": 128.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、だからあんなに練習に打ち込んでたんだな",
      "startTime": 133.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 138.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです\nリーダーとしてこのままでいいのかって焦っちゃって",
      "startTime": 140.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが個性を伸ばして、ファンがついて\n仕事が増えること自体はもちろん嬉しいんです",
      "startTime": 149.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 153.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "何より私は、四人のことを……\nその、心から尊敬してます",
      "startTime": 158.0533333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 163.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "でも、みんなが成長すればするほど\nどんどん比較して苦しくなってきて",
      "startTime": 168.31,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃……",
      "startTime": 171.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
